title: Welcome to the Winestream
author: VD
content_html:
No, not mine… Barcelona Life is picking up where I left off.

Also, due to an ongoing SJW campaign aimed at YouTube, please note that I have locked down the Darkstream channel on YouTube, so only the most recent two videos, as well as the audiobooks, are publicly accessible now. If you want to watch an older video, visit UATV or BitChute.

UPDATE: No Winestream tonight, unfortunately, due to technical difficulties.
